item.title: CVE-2019-10794|2024-08-04T22:32:01.927Z -- snyk -- component-flatten
item.description: All versions of component-flatten are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution. The a function could be tricked into adding or modifying properties of Object.prototype using a __proto__ payload.
